# Roadmap

This document is the source of truth for **project direction** — vision, strategy, phased plan. New sessions (human or AI) should read this first.

For the **why** behind specific tactical choices, see [`docs/decisions/`](./docs/decisions/). For **what landed when**, see [`CHANGELOG.md`](./CHANGELOG.md). For **what's queued but not yet built**, see [`docs/backlog/`](./docs/backlog/). The full source-of-truth set:

| Doc | Scope | Cadence |
|---|---|---|
| `ROADMAP.md` (this file) | Vision, phases, the strategic decisions D1..DN | Updated rarely; only when strategy changes |
| `docs/decisions/` | Tactical ADRs — one per non-obvious decision | One file per decision; immutable once accepted |
| `docs/backlog/` | Feedback received + improvements queued | Mutable; entries updated as work progresses |
| `docs/rubric.md` | Feature checklist (R1–R10) walked before & after every change | Stable; evolves rarely |
| `docs/learning/` | Knowledge points — transferable concepts | Append-only; new entries at meaningful moments |
| `CHANGELOG.md` | What shipped and when, organized by phase | Appended every meaningful change |

